Subject: [PATCH] Yocto: correct paths to ln and chmod
MIME-Version: 1.0
Content-Type: text/plain; charset=UTF-8
Content-Transfer-Encoding: 8bit

Change-Id: I565c665483efd43b9c5a02e8d1cc85cf6def0751
